description:
With Lychee Slicer 3, you have the very best tool to prepare your 3D models for your Resin 3D printer. 
      Youll quickly and easily define the best orientation, create and edit supports with powerful automatic or manual support generation, 
      and preview your work before exporting to your 3D printer. Lychee Slicer 3 is easy to use and provides powerful tools in an elegant, 
      refined interface. It makes your 3D printing file prep a breeze. The software is consistently being developed and updated to provide you the 
      latest innovations in 3D printing, and we have dedicated tech-support team members to assist you on your 3D printing journey. So why not start today? Lychee Slicer 
      3 is available now for free!
author: Mango3D
